OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA wet
OL,6,Fevening and night to come with the
OL,7,Frain heavy and persistent at times,
OL,8,Fespecially over the hills. Windy
OL,9,Finitially, although easing later in
OL,10,Fthe night.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA wet start, especially in the
OL,13,Feast. Rain will begin to clear from
OL,14,Fthe west though with a mix of sunshine
OL,15,Fand a few showers for the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
