OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FStaying unsettled with a mixture of
OL,7,Fsunshine and showers on Tuesday and
OL,8,FWednesday, before turning wet and
OL,9,Fwindy on Thursday. Temperatures around
OL,10,For a little below average.
